MaildirStore suse-local
Path "~/mail/suse"
Inbox "~/mail/suse/inbox"
Trash "trash"

IMAPAccount susede
Host imap.suse.de
Port 993
User "asarai@suse.de"
PassCmd +"keepassxc-helper 'Work/SUSE/SUSE Email'"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1 TLSv1.1 TLSv1.2

IMAPStore susede-remote
Account susede

Channel suse
Master :susede-remote:
Slave :suse-local:
Sync All
Expunge Both
Create Both
CopyArrivalDate yes
